{"tid":112134,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"理大學生會一號候選內閣繫理Polymer基本上係政治投機派","createTime":"2017-02-08T02:29:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-12T07:46:11.000Z","uid":14090,"like":36,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"63ccf3afeca5b771657f542b663a76170a8a897a","tid":112134,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T02:29:10.000Z","msg":"之前係政事台開左一次post 但有巴打提議係校園台開多次post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n繫理Polymer一向<strong>自稱本土</strong>，用本土個名上莊唔係問題，但佢地連本土最基本既理念都搞唔清，只係會搞臭本土個朵<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/vlzxsfbt\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fvlzxsfbt&h=371088c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n來源：蕭雲facebook page<br />\n<br />\n上面證明左佢一直自稱本土派<br />\n<br />\n但佢地連最基本既本土理念都唔知係咩，就掛本土個名出黎，博人認同<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/9fmel4ao\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F9fmel4ao&h=5af511f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n來源：蕭雲facebook page<br />\n<br />\n乜本土會支持一國兩際架咩? 我真係第一次見，一國既大前題下，本土就唔會存在，咁你講咩本土? 呢班人實際係大左膠<br />\n<br />\nOK，我地再睇睇政綱<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/iq708wob\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fiq708wob&h=0e8fb3d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家又話自己民主自決派，民主自決定本土呀屌你老母，乜撚都唔識就拎人地個名黎幫自己宣傳<br />\n<br />\n係切切實實既<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政治投機派</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n見今期興啲咩就用咩黎做政綱，我屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n利申返先，非poly學生，港獨<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母，最睇唔過眼呢啲垃圾大學生，為上莊而上莊，政治立場搞撚到亂哂，根本一班唔撚識野既MK仔上莊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-arn2-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/16508733_821354661336814_6066777253622101083_n.jpg?oh=4ffd5c58e1c3b157a653d8f939c9dc38&amp;amp;oe=5902E96D\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-arn2-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F16508733_821354661336814_6066777253622101083_n.jpg%3Foh%3D4ffd5c58e1c3b157a653d8f939c9dc38%26amp%3Boe%3D5902E96D&h=2a69ad1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位poly同學仔，認撚住呢三條MK粉皮，再呼籲你啲朋友同學唔好投比佢！！<br />\n<br />\n仲有巴打Paris比料<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7249nPA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7249nPA.jpg&h=e0c3cdec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/08/074225_96715711baddd558b77841a25e931233.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F08%2F074225_96715711baddd558b77841a25e931233.jpg&h=e52de364&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/08/074226_d74ac4bbec87344813cd89a57dbf5b9b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F08%2F074226_d74ac4bbec87344813cd89a57dbf5b9b.jpg&h=04816f19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最左果個仲係新民黨<br />\n1號個光譜闊撚到建制都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總結：繫理Polymer係政治投機派，一班MK仔借本土個名上莊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25f4878cacf78781c15760e009330a91ba32f877","tid":112134,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T02:29:27.000Z","msg":"推一推先"},{"pid":"27bded31857e843b69f9fa8661857daa2f551fee","tid":112134,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T02:31:07.000Z","msg":"繫理? 繫理老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f67b129e9229ed43595c67f385359db994bc1ba9","tid":112134,"uid":6239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T02:38:35.000Z","msg":"成班死mk<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80e18af6e11c619eb52506e7ffad42f24bd33faf","tid":112134,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T02:39:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"29c8dd07b13335051e769bdb2930739314980cd2