大學少有嘅本土撚 係呢間左膠當道政治冷感嘅野雞大學度 其實幾難得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果最後都係一三 大家OCamp照玩女照屌下莊繼續Con檯繼續反 大家開心 抵你普教中啦紅磚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5594e113b3156aa8c6c4eddf30e668e6c3b815b6","tid":112134,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T03:00:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/lq6vjgc5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Flq6vjgc5&h=a3e7e0a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n純同獨都唔係社會大眾嘅諗法? 屌你老母知唔知自己講緊咩? 又玩第三條路? 定係真建制呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"d54841a18ecf838d35daae2af7ed1b1425a0a9e8","tid":112134,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T03:01:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一號似永續社運 騎牆式嘅做法<br />\n<br />\n三號其實就應該完全冇諗過外務上嘅取態<br />\n佢哋係想永續部委姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n基本上一三號嘅政治取態<br />\n就係往年MK大學大莊兩大系統嘅延續 一邊社運一邊冷感<br />\n反而二號係呢間垃圾大學少有嘅本土撚 係呢間左膠當道政治冷感嘅野雞大學度 其實幾難得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果最後都係一三 大家OCamp照玩女照屌下莊繼續Con檯繼續反 大家開心 抵你普教中啦紅磚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n垃圾MK借本土黎呃票 佢地班mk上莊咪又係搞下OCAMP講撚到自己好熱血 最撚憎呢類人"},{"pid":"a3fcf51f42b3e52873ca7b31eb18426092705ce0","tid":112134,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T03:02:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前係政事台開左一次post 但有巴打提議係校園台開多次post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n繫理Polymer一向<strong>自稱本土</strong>，用本土個名上莊唔係問題，但佢地連本土最基本既理念都搞唔清，只係會搞臭本土個朵<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/vlzxsfbt\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fvlzxsfbt&h=371088c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n來源：蕭雲facebook page<br />\n<br />\n上面證明左佢一直自稱本土派<br />\n<br />\n但佢地連最基本既本土理念都唔知係咩，就掛本土個名出黎，博人認同<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/9fmel4ao\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F9fmel4ao&h=5af511f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n來源：蕭雲facebook page<br />\n<br />\n乜本土會支持一國兩際架咩? 我真係第一次見，一國既大前題下，本土就唔會存在，咁你講咩本土? 呢班人實際係大左膠<br />\n<br />\nOK，我地再睇睇政綱<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/iq708wob\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fiq708wob&h=0e8fb3d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家又話自己民主自決派，民主自決定本土呀屌你老母，乜撚都唔識就拎人地個名黎幫自己宣傳<br />\n<br />\n係切切實實既<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政治投機派</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n見今期興啲咩就用咩黎做政綱，我屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n利申返先，非poly學生，港獨<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母，最睇唔過眼呢啲垃圾大學生，為上莊而上莊，政治立場搞撚到亂哂，根本一班唔撚識野既MK仔上莊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7249nPA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7249nPA.jpg&h=e0c3cdec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位poly同學仔，認撚住呢三條MK粉皮，再呼籲你啲朋友同學唔好投比佢！！<br />\n<br />\n仲有巴打Paris比料<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7249nPA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7249nPA.jpg&h=e0c3cdec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/08/074225_96715711baddd558b77841a25e931233.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F08%2F074225_96715711baddd558b77841a25e931233.jpg&h=e52de364&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/08/074226_d74ac4bbec87344813cd89a57dbf5b9b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F08%2F074226_d74ac4bbec87344813cd89a57dbf5b9b.jpg&h=04816f19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最左果個仲係新民黨<br />\n1號個光譜闊撚到建制都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總結：繫理Polymer係政治投機派，一班MK仔借本土個名上莊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"2533dd49adac9a74451feab58080d6458a28a425","tid":112134,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T03:04:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/lq6vjgc5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Flq6vjgc5&h=a3e7e0a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n純同獨都唔係社會大眾嘅諗法? 屌你老母知唔知自己講緊咩? 又玩第三條路? 定係真建制呀屌你老母</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n補返source: 又係蕭雲facebook page"},{"pid":"42fb3f87da59380844dca06df4eeeb897f8a296e","tid":112134,"uid":38324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T03:04:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一號似永續社運 騎牆式嘅做法<br />\n<br />\n三號其實就應該完全冇諗過外務上嘅取態<br />\n佢哋係想永續部委姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n基本上一三號嘅政治取態<br />\n就係往年MK大學大莊兩大系統嘅延續 一邊社運一邊冷感<br />\n反而二號係呢間垃圾大學少有嘅本土撚 係呢間左膠當道政治冷感嘅野雞大學度 其實幾難得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果最後都係一三 大家OCamp照玩女照屌下莊繼續Con檯繼續反 大家開心 抵你普教中啦紅磚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n垃圾MK借本土黎呃票 佢地班mk上莊咪又係搞下OCAMP講撚到自己好熱血 最撚憎呢類人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搞Ocamp DemBeat 非常貼地非常本土 全世界得香港大學生咁撚柒 <br />\n永續搞OCamp 永續部委 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17f50d071e9f6fdec06bc03b03e82c5b4ce6a0ae","tid":112134,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T03:08:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一號似永續社運 騎牆式嘅做法<br />\n<br />\n三號其實就應該完全冇諗過外務上嘅取態<br />\n佢哋係想永續部委姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n基本上一三號嘅政治取態<br />\n就係往年MK大學大莊兩大系統嘅延續 一邊社運一邊冷感<br />\n反而二號係呢間垃圾大學少有嘅本土撚 係呢間左膠當道政治冷感嘅野雞大學度 其實幾難得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果最後都係一三 大家OCamp照玩女照屌下莊繼續Con檯繼續反 大家開心 抵你普教中啦紅磚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n垃圾MK借本土黎呃票 佢地班mk上莊咪又係搞下OCAMP講撚到自己好熱血 最撚憎呢類人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搞Ocamp DemBeat 非常貼地非常本土 全世界得香港大學生咁撚柒 <br />\n永續搞OCamp 永續部委 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搞社運離哂地 有莊就好上 要出名要成名就靠上莊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港大學生真係好撚柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我都係香港大學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d532ca43f9660136a1094b71265ac5149d49d3c1","tid":112134,"uid":21961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T03:09:03.000Z","msg":"推 等理大人見到"},{"pid":"beb677f025cc4c0047d50f230089b9f84f35c32c","tid":112134,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T03:09:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-arn2-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/16299287_257119194719669_4734571068266042005_n.jpg?oh=4df1934f84cf7efd4ad126d253d9baa7&amp;oe=5905F62F\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-arn2-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F16299287_257119194719669_4734571068266042005_n.jpg%3Foh%3D4df1934f84cf7efd4ad126d253d9baa7%26oe%3D5905F62F&h=d5b5312c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n認撚住班mk<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\